{"tid":1844990,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"點樣知道入境人士有冇去過湖北？ 陳肇始：靠佢地自己申報","createTime":"2020-01-27T01:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T03:47:44.000Z","uid":28114,"like":48,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"23a2ab95f87aa3ab6a14dfd25092ee952397cf40","tid":1844990,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T01:51:21.000Z","msg":"（超痴線！荒謬絕倫！）今朝聽香港電台《千禧年代》陳肇始局長講解關於防疫最新安排：<br />\n<br />\n主持人：點樣知道入境人士有冇去過湖北？<br />\n<br />\n陳肇：靠佢地自己申報<br />\n<br />\n主持人：點知佢講真話？<br />\n<br />\n陳肇：Er..... 我哋會度體溫，呢個係第一道防線<br />\n<br />\n主持人：如果佢發燒會點？<br />\n<br />\n陳肇：會送佢去香港嘅政府醫院隔離和接受治療<br />\n<br />\n.......<br />\n<br />\n主持人：現在見到高鐵係患者來港的主要途徑，點解張建宗上星期仲話高鐵唔需要健康申報？話驚係大堂有人群聚集？<br />\n<br />\n陳肇：我哋係收到前線人員（高鐵職員）的意見，佢地有呢個擔心；同埋申報都未必能作準....<br />\n<br />\n主持人：咁講法，咪自打嘴巴？去過湖北嘅人現在入境都一樣可以講大話？<br />\n<br />\n陳肇：Er.... <br />\n<br />\n（以上係真實對話，狠人精簡總結了....）<br />\n<br />\nRTHK：<a href=\"https://fbwat.ch/1xoehRNgqeFLXuVV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbwat.ch%2F1xoehRNgqeFLXuVV&d=0fPPgjUU32Qc%2B%2Bj2t4ropNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=efe74237\" target=\"_blank\">https://fbwat.ch/1xoehRNgqeFLXuVV</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/110776013598523/posts/177037693639021/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F110776013598523%2Fposts%2F177037693639021%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=0fPPgjUU32Qc%2B%2Bj2t4ropNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=0c0783dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/110776013598523/posts/177037693639021/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"ec846aa7a1884c8024557096a5d88b229328dbb6","tid":1844990,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T01:55:35.000Z","msg":"（取笑系列）抗爭者真係好垃圾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844940</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8d388e688d05425a4632c251804a6a50151b0da1","tid":1844990,"uid":28114,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T02:02:39.000Z","